\"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kangaroo\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"her chin\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"stage\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"another B-girl\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, her unorthodox performance attracted a mixture of praise and ridicule.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her unorthodox performance\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"a mixture\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"ridicule\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She spoke to Network Ten'sThe Projectabout the response she had received.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Network\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"the response\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is really sad to hear those criticisms,\\\" the lecturer in the Department of Media, Communications, Creative Arts, Language and Literature at Macquarie University Faculty of Arts told host Waleed Aly.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waleed_Aly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Waleed Aly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waleed_Aly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waleed_Aly\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those criticisms\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"the lecturer\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the Department\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"Media\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"Communications\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"Creative Arts\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"Language\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"Literature\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"Macquarie University Faculty\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"Arts\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I am very sorry for the backlash that the community has experienced, but I can not control how people react.\\\"\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn also explained that having people chase her left her in a \\\"state of panic\\\".\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gunn\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"state\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"panic\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, when asked if she was Australia's best female breakdancer, she said: \\\"I think my record speaks to that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9976028598651694, \"rank\": 0.0019625141431799634, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my record\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She previously addressed her evocative performance on social media.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her evocative performance\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said in August: \\\"I just want to start by thanking all the people who have supported me.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really appreciate the positivity, and I am glad I was able to bring some joy into your lives.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the positivity\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"some joy\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1743}, {\"ngram\": \"your lives\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's what I hoped.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not realise that that would also open the door to so much hate, which has, frankly, been pretty devastating.\\\"\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"so much hate\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I went out there and I had fun.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for theOlympics, and I gave my all,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my butt\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breakdancing originated as a counterculture dance form from the US and is associated with the hip-hop community.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2114, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9986727477969354, \"rank\": 0.0013236285176688402, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a counterculture dance form\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"the hip-hop community\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is competitively known as breaking and joined skateboarding, sport climbing, and surfing in making its debut at the 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"sport climbing\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, some critics questioned breaking's role as an Olympic sport following Gunn's performance.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some critics\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking's role\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"Gunn's performance\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another standout moment from the breaking competition was the disqualification of Afghan athlete Manizha Talash, who wore a cape that said \\\"free Afghan women\\\".\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghans\", \"score\": 0.9995421138790657, \"rank\": 0.0004580538508511425, \"text\": \"Afghan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghans\"}, {\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manizha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\",